, 51, 51); text-decoration-line: none;\">transactions</a>, et l\'osmose entre les personnes se ressent dansla qualit&eacute; de l\'accueil et de l\'&eacute;coute du client, notre priorit&eacute; &eacute;tant de satisfaire sa demande.</div></div></div>    \r\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; width: 1170px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" open=\"\" sans?,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 13px;?=\"\">    \r\n<div class=\"row-fluid block_footer\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px 5px; width: 1170px; font-size: 0.9em;\">    \r\n<div class=\"span4\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/RealEstateAgent\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; float: left; min-height: 30px; width: 370px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong itemprop=\"name\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.2em;\">AFIM MONACO</strong><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /><span itemprop=\"address\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/PostalAddress\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span itemprop=\"streetAddress\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Les Floralies, 3 Avenue de Grande Bretagne</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /><span itemprop=\"postalCode\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">98000</span>&nbsp;-&nbsp;<span itemprop=\"addressLocality\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">MONACO</span>&nbsp;<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /></span>T&eacute;l.&nbsp;<span itemprop=\"telephone\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">003 77 97 97 87 87</span>&nbsp;- Fax. 003 77 97 97 87 88&nbsp;<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /><a itemprop=\"email\" title=\"annonces immobilières Monaco\" href=\"http://www.afim.mc/nous-contacter.html\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-decoration-line: none;\">afim@afim.mc</a></div>    \r\n<div class=\"span4 logo-bas\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; float: left; min-height: 30px; width: 370px; position: relative; text-align